headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 3X GTA$ and RP on Extraction
content:
All Extraction players will earn 3X GTA$ and RP this week. Plus, to sweeten the deal, competitors who win three rounds of Extraction will also receive a lump sum bonus of GTA$150K, delivered within 72 hours of completion.

To launch Extraction, head to the Online tab in the Pause Menu. Locate Rockstar Created and discover maps in the Adversary Mode menu list.
